# borisRo — Photography Portfolio Website

## Project Overview

A modern, minimal photography portfolio website for the brand **borisRo**. Built with Next.js 16, React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, and Framer Motion. Inspired by sites like GuruShots, 500px, and Aperture.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 16 (App Router, `src/` directory)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 (using `@theme inline` and CSS variables)
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Fonts**: Inter (latin, cyrillic), Heebo (hebrew)
- **Images**: Unsplash (remote), local images in `public/images/`

## Multi-Language Support (i18n)

Three languages: **English (en)**, **Hebrew (he)**, **Russian (ru)**
- Translations defined in `src/lib/translations.ts` as a flat object keyed by section
- `t()` helper function takes a translation key record and a Lang
- Hebrew triggers RTL layout via `document.documentElement.dir = "rtl"`
- Uses CSS logical properties (`ms-`, `me-`, `start`, `end`) for RTL compatibility
- Language persisted in `localStorage` as `borisro-lang`
- Heebo font used for Hebrew, Inter for English/Russian

## Theme Support

Two themes: **dark** and **light**
- Controlled via `data-theme` attribute on `<html>`
- CSS variables switch automatically between themes in `globals.css`
- Theme persisted in `localStorage` as `borisro-theme`
- Dark is default

## Project Structure

```
src/
  app/
    layout.tsx       — Root layout, Inter + Heebo fonts, AppProvider wrapper
    page.tsx         — Main page composing all sections
    globals.css      — Tailwind imports, CSS variables for both themes, animations
  lib/
    translations.ts  — All translations (EN/HE/RU), t() helper, isRTL()
    context.tsx      — AppProvider with lang/theme state, localStorage persistence, dir/lang attributes
  components/
    Logo.tsx         — Pure text wordmark "borisRo" (no SVG icon)
    Header.tsx       — Fixed header, blur on scroll, mobile menu, language selector (Globe + dropdown on desktop, pill buttons on mobile), theme toggle (Sun/Moon)
    Hero.tsx         — Full-screen image slideshow, translated subtitle + CTA
    Gallery.tsx      — Photo grid, translated filters/titles/categories, lightbox
    Categories.tsx   — 6 collection cards with translated names
    About.tsx        — Photographer photo + translated bio + stats
    Contact.tsx      — Translated form labels + button
    Footer.tsx       — Translated copyright
public/
  images/
    photographer.png — Photographer's personal portrait photo
```

## Design System

- **Dark theme**: bg `#090909`, text `#e8e8e8`, card `#111111`
- **Light theme**: bg `#fafafa`, text `#1a1a1a`, card `#f0f0f0`
- **Color palette**: Monochromatic — no accent colors
- **Typography**: Inter (200-700), Heebo for Hebrew
- **Layout**: Max width 1400px, 1px gaps between grid items, CSS logical properties for RTL
- **Hover states**: Subtle scale (1.03) + dark overlay on images
- **Transitions**: Background/color transitions on theme switch (0.3s)

## External Image Domains

Configured in `next.config.ts`: `images.unsplash.com`, `plus.unsplash.com`
